Battera::

She smiled and blushed slightly. "Oh, I've never heard of them. Are 
they a good faction to work for?"  She rubbed her hands nervously, 
and smiled up at Starscream. "Uh, forgive my, I should thank you for 
saving as you did. It was very nice of you to do that for me. Thank 
you."

He seamed like a nice bot to her.  She was a pred, but most of her 
programming had been neutralized.  She was mostly a neutral bot now.  
She did find this bot atractive, but she was scared at the same time.
"AH, well, I don't what else I could do for you. I guess this is 
where we part way then?" she phrased more like a question than a 
statement.
